node.title: Truck and trailer unit rolls into Waioeka Gorge river
node.description: Emergency services are responding to the incident in the Bay of Plenty.
node.content:
["Emergency services are responding to a serious crash in the Bay of Plenty's Waioeka Gorge.", "", "
Police says there are indications injuries have been sustained in the crash. Photo: St John / Lee Howell
", "A truck and trailer unit has rolled into the river off Waioeka Road.", "Police said in a statement that the crash was reported to them just before midday and there were indications injuries had been sustained.", "The gorge, which forms part of State Highway 2 between Ōpōtiki and Gisborne, is expected to be closed and motorists are asked to delay travel."]
